### 用来向认证中心获取授权
GET http://localhost:8082/authserver/oauth/authorize?client_id=client1&client_secret=secret&response_type=code&scope=all&redirect_uri=http://www.baidu.com
Accept: application/json

### 获取token
POST http://client1:secret@localhost:8082/authserver/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "client_id" : "client1",
  "client_secret" : "secret",
  "grant_type" : "authorization_code",
  "code": "LBxSox",
  "redirect_uri" : "http://www.baidu.com",
  "score" : "all"
}


